Subject: drm/amd/powerplay: fix performance drop on Vega10
Git-commit: b87079ec7b4d38efee015367315958ce5495ba93
Patch-mainline: v4.15-rc1
References: FATE#326289 FATE#326079 FATE#326049 FATE#322398 FATE#326166

Setting package power PID to 1 fixes performance drop caused by
updated SMU FW, before DPM is enabled.

